Transform Node: Transform the Data Before Loading It Into a Target

Use a Transform node in CRM Analytics to manipulate data based on the transformations added. You can add one or more transformations to each Transform node.

Select the Add Node button between two nodes or at the end of the recipe. Select Transform in the Add Node dialog box. Select one or more columns for which you want to transform their data.

Use the Transform toolbar to add a transformation based on the selected columns. Each time you add a transformation, it appears in the left panel as a step.

To preview the results of a transformation, select the step in the left panel. View the Graph area by clicking the Collapse button. Preview results for each node and transformation to ensure expected results.

Add more transformations to the Transform node if needed. Save the recipe.
